{"tid":154891,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"任天堂 Switch  已遭破解 ! JB 工具成功運行","createTime":"2017-03-13T15:25:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T17:39:13.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d938c688a75514efa724eb041acb3859df58db2","tid":154891,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T15:25:29.000Z","msg":"三月 13, 2017 &bull; 遊戲情報 &bull;<br />\n<br />\n不論任何電子產品的系統都可能會存在漏洞，而黑客往往會善加利用。比如任天堂最新款主機 Switch 雖然只推出了個數星期，但黑客已發現到裡面的隱藏瀏覽器竟出現了一大堆舊有的漏洞，而且更成功透過這些漏洞在 Switch 上運行類似越獄工具，說不定這款新主機很快便會被人破解。<br />\n<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/001-61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2F001-61.jpg&h=6bdab8ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n著名黑客 qwertyoruiop 過往曾參與過多個 iOS 版本及 PS4 的越獄（Jailbreak）工作，至於近日他就發現到 Switch 原來都有不少漏洞。雖然現階段 qwertyoruiop 並未有提供詳細方法及證據，但據知他首先稍微修改現有的 jailbreakMe iOS Webkit，將當中特定的 iOS 代碼刪除，然後再成功在 Switch 上運行。<br />\n<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/002-42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2F002-42.jpg&h=5241f1c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然今次這種入侵只屬於用戶級別，而並未去到可獲得更多控制權的內核漏洞級別，但可以想像得到應該還有更多黑客在查找類似的漏洞。而 qwertyoruiop 亦已經開始作更深研究，並發現到 Switch 的 syscall 並不像建基於 FreeBSD，反而更似是 3DS 系統代碼的變更。留意由於今次這批漏洞已經被公開，相信任天堂很快便會發佈更新去修復，而一如過往黑客與任天堂之間的攻防戰亦似乎正式展開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/03/13/nintendo-switch-webkit-vulnerability/game-channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F03%2F13%2Fnintendo-switch-webkit-vulnerability%2Fgame-channel%2F&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=ae81e919\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/03/13/nintendo-switch-webkit-vulnerability/game-channel/</a>"},{"pid":"d29edb300c51c3e27f35c4f7a52347951e936f3f","tid":154891,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T15:53:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e6f9876c0fc79754b5157bb8f76f50380ee8d52","tid":154891,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T15:59:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca421cb71285d859b560e6230c6d7307f741ab5","tid":154891,"uid":28878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T15:59:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27154f4425a45e8821e50a1442668c899c3e0d39","tid":154891,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:35:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25af3a4b4bbdcb3aa386e3911f1f10261ffed087","tid":154891,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T17:21:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d12ae0b1e7b403cb0853f8284ca717f7bb68d02e","tid":154891,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T17:30:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=00430&amp;snA=41226\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D00430%26snA%3D41226&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=a52d3f1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=00430&amp;snA=41226</a>"},{"pid":"9da4fabc4e9381b87b4b13ffd729466c74531fc5","tid":154891,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T18:42:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35cff0b0dfccdf8bf5d009add9f94643be11c598","tid":154891,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T18:48:25.000Z","msg":"老任<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e423e963e06f8f3f240684c15f7b43aaea6d136","tid":154891,"uid":476,"lik